# text = tasyāṃ ca kumudadhūlidhavalena bhasmanā likhitasya mahato maṇḍalasya madhye sthitaṃ dīptataratejaḥprasaram pṛthupariveṣaparikṣiptam iva śaratsavitāram mathyamānakṣīrodāvartavartinam iva mandaram raktacandanānulepino raktasragambarābharaṇasyottānaśayasya śavasyorasy upaviśya jātajātavedasi mukhakuhare prārabdhāgnikāryam kṛṣṇoṣṇīṣam kṛṣṇāṅgarāgam kṛṣṇapratisaram kṛṣṇavāsasam kṛṣṇatilāhutinibhena vidyādharatvatṛṣṇayā mānuṣanirmāṇakāraṇakāluṣyaparamāṇūn iva kṣayam upanayantam āhutidānaparyastābhiḥ pretamukhasparśadūṣitaṃ prakṣālayantam ivāśuśukṣaṇiṃ karanakhadīdhitibhiḥ dhūmālohitena cakṣuṣā kṣatajāhutim iva hutabhuji pātayantam īṣadvivṛtādharapuṭaprakaṭitasitadaśanaśikhareṇa dṛśyamānamūrtamantrākṣarapaṅktineva mukhena kim api japantam homaśramasvedasalilapratibimbitābhir āsannadīpikābhir dahantam iva karmasiddhaye sarvāvayavān aṃsāvalambinā bahuguṇena vidyārājeneva brahmasūtreṇa parigṛhītaṃ bhairavācāryam apaśyat
